data.description: This home with over an acre is so quiet & private, yet so convenient to shopping, schools, highway commuting, etc! Covered front porch greets you, then enter into the large living room with vaulted ceiling and wood fireplace. Kitchen has ample storage & baker's island. Primary bedroom separated from other bedrooms and features large walk-in closet, separate tub/shower, and make-up vanity. Outside there are 2 apple trees, flowering cherry & plum, flower beds, arbor and the roof is less than a 3-years old. Ready to move into before the December holidays!
